summary:
We help fast growing FinTech, SaaS, Cyber and eCommerce companies to find the talent that will take their organization to the next level and get exposure through our podcast, magazine and webinars.  

Are you an executive or founder:
- Who has high growth plans for your teams or company? 
- Who is struggling to find the high-caliber candidates who can take your organization to the next level? 
- Who does not have the time to speak to people who are not relevant to what you are looking for?  

Our sole purpose is to help our clients find the people who will contribute to and can accelerate their growth. 

For over 10 years we have placed exclusively in the FinTech, Saas, Cyber and eCom industries across Europe, US and APAC. 

We have placed over 1000 people in these respective industries with a 92% retention rate. 

Our process is simple: 
1. We set up a discovery call to discuss the job profile, candidate requirements, interview process, salary and delivery timeline. 
2. We start headhunting and present the first shortlist of candidates within 10 days. 
3. We have a weekly catch-up call to discuss interview feedback and next steps. 
4. We present and manage the job offer and assist with (remote) onboarding.

If you would like to know more about how we can help you, send me a DM or email me at rogier@teampcn.com. 

If you are interested in hearing more about our In Check with FinTech podcast, our industry events or webinars, email us at marketing@teampcn.com and find out more about the podcast here:
https://teampcn.com/podcasts/
